    {
      "_id": "6kmY491GZA7iqp6g",
      "name": "Portable Power (Ex)",
      "type": "feat",
      "data": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>&gt;<a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"sfrpg.class-features\" data-id=\"YMGOKoZtKgJqIsAD\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Mechanic Trick</a></p>\n        <p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl14_LabelName\">You can use your custom rig to supply limited power for up to 1 minute to a computer or starship system that lacks power. If this system is part of a much larger network, this trick does not supply power to the entire network, just to a limited point of access (typically a terminal), which might greatly limit functionality. Once you have used portable power on a system, you cannot do so again on that system for 24 hours.</span></p>",
